  <brief_title>HINTEGRA Total Ankle Prosthesis Follow-up</brief_title>
  <official_title>Short to Mid Term Follow-up of Patient Implanted With the HINTEGRA® Total Ankle Prosthesis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
